subject: Indianapolis 500 (Auto Race)
Automobile Racing
lead_paragraph: The 28-year-old Indianapolis rookie Raphael Matos led the second day of qualifying for the Indy 500 on Sunday, posting a four-lap average of 223.429 miles an hour to top the second group of 11 drivers to make it into the 33-car field for the May 24 race.
